These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, handball
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | mirinda | fanta | hot-chocolate   |
| Sport      | sailing    | snowboarding  | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, coffee
There are 3 different nationalities: american, brazilian, indian
1. the american is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the brazilian is on the far left##1
3. the brazilian is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | water     | coffee      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | american | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, mirinda, juice
There 3 different types of food: pomegranate, cauliflower, kale
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person eating kale##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage   | milk | juice  | mirinda       |
| Food       | pomegranate     | cauliflower | kale |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, lime, corn
The people have 3 different hobbies: video-games, reading, filmmaking
1. the person eating lime is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person eating mango is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Food    | corn    | lime     | mango |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | video-games | reading     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, fish, lizard
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, roller, scooter
1. the person driving the roller is the owner of the lizard##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
4. the owner of the mouse is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | fish | mouse     | lizard |
| Transport   | scooter        | subway | roller    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, potato, pumpkin
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, bus, jet-ski
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the person eating potato is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person eating pumpkin is the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | pumpkin | artichoke      | potato  |
| Transport   | quad-bike       | bus | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, electronic
3 different pets are kept: hamster, bird, dog
1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the fan of folk is the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic      | blues     | folk    |
| Pet           | hamster | dog | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
