2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
3. the person eating watermelon is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | zucchini | lettuce | watermelon      |
| Hobby   | board-games     | gardening | reading |

