3 different pets are kept: turtle, fish, dog
1. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the owner of the fish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Hobby   | camping | magic-tricks | gardening  |
| Pet     | dog     | turtle      | fish |

