.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, spy, superhero
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | coffee   | iced-tea    | hot-chocolate    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | epic | superhero |

