There are 3 different nationalities: indonesian, indian, australian
1. the fan of techno is the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the australian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | house | techno   | hip-hop  |
| Nationality   | australian    | indonesian | indian |

