The people have 3 different jobs:  photographer, lawyer, freelancer
1. the lawyer is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating papaya is in the middle##1
3. the photographer is on the right of the person eating papaya##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
