.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, hot-chocolate, coffee
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, jazz, r&b
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | milk  | coffee | hot-chocolate  |
| Music-Genre   | jazz | r&b   | soul |

