1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person eating apple is the person who's sport is swimming##1
3. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | pepper | lettuce   | apple        |
| Sport   | rugby    | soccer | swimming |

