.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, fishing, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, ambient, dubstep
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the fan of dubstep##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | photography | fishing | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | dubstep     | ambient  |

