.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, tomato, raspberry
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, skateboarding, lacrosse
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | raspberry | mango       | tomato  |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | skateboarding | baseball |

 